                                    <p class="has-medium-font-size">Gluteus</p>
                                    <p class="has-small-font-size"><p>Large, superficial muscles located at your buttocks just below your lower back area.</p></p>
                                </div>
                                                            <div class="secondary-item muscle-item">
                                    <div class="muscle-img">
                                        <img src="https://www.endomondo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Hip-Adductors.png" alt="">
                                    </div>
                                    <p class="has-medium-font-size">Hip Adductors</p>
                                    <p class="has-small-font-size"><p><span data-sheets-root="\&quot;1\&quot;" data-sheets-value="\&quot;{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;Muscles" data-sheets-userformat="\&quot;{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:0},&quot;11&quot;:3,&quot;12&quot;:0}\&quot;">Muscles located at the upper inside part of your legs between your quads and hamstrings. </span></p></p>
                                </div>
